<dl id="n11114c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n11" href="#n11114c">N11 (VI.B.5)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n11all.htm#n11114c"> 114(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> refuse cart to / meet tourists</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">&lsquo;CRYING GRIEVANCE&rsquo; / The Need for More Houses in / Galway. / <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> / Mr. Young said a good deal of the blame for the condition of the streets was to be placed on the shoulders of their own officials. <mark>It was no time to be bringing the refuse cart out at 11 o&apos;clock in the morning to meet visitors on the mail train</mark> (laughter). <small> <a name="CT5jul24" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#CT5jul24"><cite title="source">Connacht Tribune</cite></a> (5 July 1924) 5/5</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
